app = read.csv("/Users/macintosh/Desktop/Northwestern/2019\ Spring\ Quarter/462\ Marketing\ Models/Assignment\ 2/app.csv"
               , header = T)
library(plm)
library(MatchIt)
library(MASS)
#########
#data transformation check
par(mfrow = c(1,3))
for(i in 9:11){
  hist(app[,i], xlab = names(app)[i])
}

for(i in 12:14){
  hist(app[,i], xlab = names(app)[i])
}

for(i in 15:17){
  hist(app[,i], xlab = names(app)[i])
}

for(i in 18:20){
  hist(app[,i], xlab = names(app)[i])
}

par(mfrow = c(1,1))
hist(app$n_non_kakao)

summary(app$gender)
##    Length     Class      Mode

################
#variable creation
app$t_total_game = app$t_anipang + app$t_kakao_game + app$t_non_kakao_game
app$t_total_story = app$t_kakao_story + app$t_non_kakao_story


##################
#subset selection 1 , all data set
app.beforetrt = subset(app, week ==1)
set.seed(12345)
#PSM 1to1, replacement, caliper = 0, final.dat1.p
NN1.out= matchit(tg ~ age + income + education + gender + t_kakao_talk + t_anipang + t_kakao_story + 
                   t_kakao_game + n_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_game + n_non_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_story
                 +n_non_kakao_story + t_non_kakao_talk + n_non_kakao_talk + t_non_kakao + n_non_kakao, data = app.beforetrt, method = "nearest",
                 ratio = 1, replace = T, )
m.dat1  = match.data(NN1.out)
ID1.dat = m.dat1["panel_id"]
final.dat1  = merge(app, ID1.dat, by = "panel_id")
final.dat1.p = pdata.frame(final.dat1, index = c("panel_id","week"))

#PSM 1to1,  replacement, caliper = 0.2, final.dat2.p
NN2.out= matchit(tg ~ age + income + education + gender + t_kakao_talk + t_anipang + t_kakao_story + 
                   t_kakao_game + n_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_game + n_non_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_story
                 +n_non_kakao_story + t_non_kakao_talk + n_non_kakao_talk + t_non_kakao + n_non_kakao, data = app.beforetrt, method = "nearest",
                 ratio = 1, replace = T,caliper = 0.2 )
m.dat2  = match.data(NN2.out)
ID2.dat = m.dat2["panel_id"]
final.dat2  = merge(app, ID2.dat, by = "panel_id")
final.dat2.p = pdata.frame(final.dat2, index = c("panel_id","week"))


#PSM 1to1,  no replacement, caliper = 0, final.dat3.p
NN3.out= matchit(tg ~ age + income + education + gender + t_kakao_talk + t_anipang + t_kakao_story + 
                   t_kakao_game + n_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_game + n_non_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_story
                 +n_non_kakao_story + t_non_kakao_talk + n_non_kakao_talk + t_non_kakao + n_non_kakao, data = app.beforetrt, method = "nearest",
                 ratio = 1, replace = F )

m.dat3  = match.data(NN3.out)
ID3.dat = m.dat3["panel_id"]
final.dat3  = merge(app, ID3.dat, by = "panel_id")
final.dat3.p = pdata.frame(final.dat3, index = c("panel_id","week"))


#PSM 1to1, no replacement, caliper = 0.2, final.dat4.p
NN4.out= matchit(tg ~ age + income + education + gender + t_kakao_talk + t_anipang + t_kakao_story + 
                   t_kakao_game + n_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_game + n_non_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_story
                 +n_non_kakao_story + t_non_kakao_talk + n_non_kakao_talk + t_non_kakao + n_non_kakao, data = app.beforetrt, method = "nearest",
                 ratio = 1, replace = F, caliper = 0.2 )

m.dat4  = match.data(NN4.out)
ID4.dat = m.dat4["panel_id"]
final.dat4  = merge(app, ID4.dat, by = "panel_id")
final.dat4.p = pdata.frame(final.dat4, index = c("panel_id","week"))



####### subset selection and PSM
#total_game_percent
app.percentgame = subset(app, app$t_total_game>0)
app.percentgame$game_percent = (app.percentgame$t_anipang+app.percentgame$t_kakao_game)/app.percentgame$t_total_game
app.beforetrt1 = subset(app.percentgame, week ==1)

#PSM 1to1, replacement, caliper = 0, final.dat1game.p
NN1game.out= matchit(tg ~ age + income + education + gender + t_kakao_talk + t_anipang + t_kakao_story + 
                   t_kakao_game + n_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_game + n_non_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_story
                 +n_non_kakao_story + t_non_kakao_talk + n_non_kakao_talk + t_non_kakao + n_non_kakao, data = app.beforetrt1, method = "nearest",
                 ratio = 1, replace = T, )
m.dat1game  = match.data(NN1game.out)
ID1game.dat = m.dat1game["panel_id"]
final.dat1game  = merge(app.percentgame, ID1game.dat, by = "panel_id")
final.dat1game.p = pdata.frame(final.dat1game, index = c("panel_id","week"))

#PSM 1to1,  replacement, caliper = 0.2, final.dat2game.p
NN2game.out= matchit(tg ~ age + income + education + gender + t_kakao_talk + t_anipang + t_kakao_story + 
                       t_kakao_game + n_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_game + n_non_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_story
                     +n_non_kakao_story + t_non_kakao_talk + n_non_kakao_talk + t_non_kakao + n_non_kakao, data = app.beforetrt1, method = "nearest",
                     ratio = 1, replace = T,caliper = 0.2 )
m.dat2game  = match.data(NN2game.out)
ID2game.dat = m.dat2game["panel_id"]
final.dat2game  = merge(app.percentgame, ID2game.dat, by = "panel_id")
final.dat2game.p = pdata.frame(final.dat2game, index = c("panel_id","week"))


#PSM 1to1,  no replacement, caliper = 0, final.dat3game.p
NN3game.out= matchit(tg ~ age + income + education + gender + t_kakao_talk + t_anipang + t_kakao_story + 
                   t_kakao_game + n_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_game + n_non_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_story
                 +n_non_kakao_story + t_non_kakao_talk + n_non_kakao_talk + t_non_kakao + n_non_kakao, data = app.beforetrt1, method = "nearest",
                 ratio = 1, replace = F )

m.dat3game  = match.data(NN3game.out)
ID3game.dat = m.dat3game["panel_id"]
final.dat3game  = merge(app.percentgame, ID3game.dat, by = "panel_id")
final.dat3game.p = pdata.frame(final.dat3game, index = c("panel_id","week"))


#PSM 1to1, no replacement, caliper = 0.2, final.dat4game.p
NN4game.out= matchit(tg ~ age + income + education + gender + t_kakao_talk + t_anipang + t_kakao_story + 
                   t_kakao_game + n_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_game + n_non_kakao_game + t_non_kakao_story
                 +n_non_kakao_story + t_non_kakao_talk + n_non_kakao_talk + t_non_kakao + n_non_kakao, data = app.beforetrt1, method = "nearest",
                 ratio = 1, replace = F, caliper = 0.2 )

m.dat4game  = match.data(NN4.out)
ID4game.dat = m.dat4game["panel_id"]

final.dat4game.p = pdata.frame(final.dat4game, index = c("panel_id","week"))


#####total_story_percent
app.percentstory = subset(app, app$t_total_story>0)
app.percentstory$story_percent = app.percentstory$t_kakao_story/app.percentstory$t_total_story
app.beforetrt2 = subset(app.percentstory, week ==1)

#PSM 1to1,  replacement, caliper = 0.2, final.dat2story.p
